cors-proxy-sdk: pluggable fetch SDK over a registry of public CORS proxies. Core in src/: types.ts (ProxyDescriptor transform/untransform/caps), registry.ts (8 builtins: codetabs,corsproxy-io,allorigins-get,allorigins-raw,cors-sh,cors-anywhere-herokuapp,thingproxy,whateverorigin), client.ts (CorsProxyClient + createProxiedFetch; strategies first-healthy/round-robin/random/race; per-attempt timeout+abort; 429/403 cooldown demotion), errors.ts (AllProxiesFailedError). Tests: test/sdk.test.ts (vitest, 14) + test.js (real codetabs integration witness). Build tsup ESM+CJS+dts. No git remote provisioned yet - commits local.